  "text": "Sequence analysis. Sequences were assembled and analysed using Lasergene software version 6.0 (DNASTAR Inc.) and MEGA version 4 [CITATION_1] . Sequence alignments were performed using the CLUSTAL V algorithm in Lasergene.",
